Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:14.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate was about to welcome \Na rare, peaceful morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:18.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he had no way \Nof knowing that this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,would turn out to be a life-altering day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, why don't we go to the primary family \Nresidence for once, where your grandfather resides?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... I would like \Nintroduce Hayate as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to express \Nsuch undisguised loathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather Mikado, the head \Nof the Sanzenin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head of the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the person currently in possession \Nof the Sanzenin family estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I could end up getting \Nfired if I make the wrong impression...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he could easily wipe you \Noff the face of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:15.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:19.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:23.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human body holds untold powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you train, the more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:36.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:36.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:43.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:43.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:51.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:51.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:55.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:55.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:04.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:04.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:14.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:14.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:20.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:20.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:32.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:32.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:39.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:39.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:46.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:46.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.46,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}The Value of My Life: Priceless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we hired a new butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's any need to pay our \Nrespects to that old geezer at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandfather is the only \Nimmediate family you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's been a long time \Nsince I've seen Grandpa Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Never mind all that. \NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! I'm related to the \NSanzenin family, too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what kind of man is your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were Dragon Quest, he'd be Zoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the traditional storytelling \Nworld, he'd be Danshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will I do okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting such a terrifying sounding person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya offend him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that man could easily crush \Nan indebted butler's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's da man who destroyed Compile,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just 'cause Puyo Pop was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Nomura Toys' \Ndownfall was also 'cause of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case, he's \Nkind of a fiendish guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so try not to be taken in if \Nhe says anything odd to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know, it's not the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the poisonous-apple-eating \Nprincess of the mouse kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Mikado Sanzenin. \NThis is her grandfather's primary residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... So, what country are we in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What line of work is your grandfather in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Oil baron, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not a line of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hayate was belatedly \Ncoming to the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Nagi was not just your \Nrun-of-the-mill rich girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that she was an INCREDIBLY rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But talk about a stuffy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Sakuya and Maria, it \Nis good of you to come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I apologize for disturbing \Nyou upon your return, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with this \Nsuspicious individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had snuck aboard the chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks incredibly suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can appreciate your sentiment, but \Nhe's not a suspicious individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Himegami's successor \Nand he serves as my butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shabby-looking man, who \Nseems to have no luck with money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... um... that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hayate put up with the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he most certainly did \Nnot have any luck with money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:46.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and there was no question \Nthat he was shabby-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to emphasize it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, that was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Saku, don't laugh at him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the start that \NI didn't fit in here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just called it like they saw it. \NThere was no malice behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right. You will only waste \Nyour time letting it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm 150 million yen in debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do I really look like I \Nhave such poor luck with money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are more important \Nthings than money, like compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each individual must be considerate \Nof the planet's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They won't look me in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, being dressed like that for your \Nmeeting with your grandfather is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to change, so go \Nget some fresh air or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this is a belated realization,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to let a man like me, \Nso deeply in debt, run loose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this place packed full of \Ntreasures seems far too imprudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something of value?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes a good sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece alone just might be able \Nto pay off my 150 million yen debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At best, that vase will fetch \N5 million on Yahoo Auctions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you won't be able to pay off your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! It was \Njust an impulsive thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry. I can \Ntell, just by looking at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're not the kind of person \Nwho would do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Don't look at me like, \N"What's this senile old man saying?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of this household.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking care of the yard right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're a gardener.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear... You don't have \Nfaith in my insight, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll show you just \Nhow formidable my insight is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so come along with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:15.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This old man's smile sparkles \Nlike that of a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Maria, this outfit is a bit big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just peeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To train one's insight, \None must work daily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after working daily, what kind \Nof criminal do you intend to become?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is someone like you doing \Nwith a debt of 150 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally my parents' gambling debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are incredible good-for-nothings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they gifted me to some "very \Ngenerous people" as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Miss Nagi took on that debt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, I am in the process \Nof returning it over 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really grateful to Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So grandpa, you mustn't peep at her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life is utterly meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully insipid for a man \Nthat Nagi's placed her faith in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My insight is the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bursting of the bubble, \Nthe change in government,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even Toshi losing his hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I anticipated it all with these eyes of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the unprecedented little sister boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I foresaw its coming since before the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these eyes are telling me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is even more meaningless \Nthan the lives of your scummy parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mikado Sanzenin, assure you that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A life spent merely for the \Nsake of repaying a debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is utterly meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you still wish to make \Nyour life something of value...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a levitation stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That is your guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe that your \Nlife may yet have meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do not lose it, do not \Nlet it be taken from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it with you until the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you are able to obtain the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of the road that it leads you to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never mind 150 million. A \Nbillion! Even 10 billion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of that will surely be within your reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:15.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the meaning of his life \Ndenied in its entirety,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will Hayate be able to \Nbegin walking down the road
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}shown to him by the pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be continued in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria, are we okay with \Nnot having a punch line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have not had much of a punch \Nline in the past, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! If there isn't at \Nleast one punch line a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Kansai person's blood starts to tingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run! It won't make for a punch line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That punch line is already an empty shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say this to you, it is garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaddup! Punch it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lambada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby boomer generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Granddaughter, do you want to \Ninherit the Sanzenin family fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it means that you'll \Nbe dying soon, I'd welcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! O Maria! My granddaughter \Nis being mean to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, now that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, never mind the fortune, \Ncan I get some pocket change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even without all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I have the World Business \NSatellite show and the stock market,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never have money problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Uselessly gaining more \Nand more knowledge every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who had me educated \Nso that would happen, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall teaching you \Nto draw such worthless manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.38,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Seen From Below
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.38,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,137)}Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you \Nget a hold of my manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter really {\i1}is{\i0} mean to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Grandfather, why did \Nyou suddenly bring this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the truth is, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nagi will end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.17,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Loser Park
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.11,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,-inner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There it is again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I got it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.55,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ominous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:46.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I ever thought about was money, \Nbecause of the way my parents were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd never even thought about my own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:53.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But am I okay with my life being like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:57.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A life spent solely for the \Npurpose of repaying debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's hurry up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can't put up with that \Nstinking old geezer anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something did happen... \NOr rather, will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is about to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wha... Who is this person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! So he's really come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite skilled to \Ndodge Gilbert's sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is this fake-sounding foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's a long story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who may inherit all \Nof the Sanzenin family fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inherit it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:10.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The story will grind to a halt if \Nwe leave the explanation to Nagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:14.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so we will have you watch the \Nrest of the earlier scene here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Grandfather, why did \Nyou suddenly bring this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the truth is, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nagi will end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why would I end up dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finally gone senile, \Nyou stinking old geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not gone senile, nor do I stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it, Granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once I die, the family fortune \Nwill go to you in its entirety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, many of our relatives \Ndo not favor this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people out there who would \Nsell their son for 150 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it seems plausible that some \Nmay try to take Nagi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came up with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone can fulfill a certain condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would leave the Sanzenin \Nfamily fortune, not to Nagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to that person instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho. And what is this condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this condition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the family fortune to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please have mercy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and make you apologize in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.24,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,The Tail Wagging the Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than spout \Nsuch embarrassing lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand the things \Nthat rich people come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry, I don't understand it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that being the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please apologize in tears to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm apologizing to you! Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please apologize in tears to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you have any pride or anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such things is \Nuseless! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Old Man Mikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just beat that weak-looking \Nbutler to a pulp,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a chance that the Miss \Nmight apologize in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna beat the crap outta him \Nand make the family fortune mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the Miss can no longer inherit \Nthe Sanzenin family fortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that means she won't be enormously \Nrich like she is now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that were to happen, \Nwould this girl be alone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rendered homeless, like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rice porridge is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Maria, for all the \Ntrouble I'm putting you through...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised not to talk about that, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Hayate would pay you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have lent him \Nthat 150 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That could be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to meet your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Money! Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A life spent merely for the \Nsake of repaying a debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is utterly meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Miss came to my rescue, wearing \Nthat silly-looking mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Miss put her heart and soul \Ninto nursing me back to health...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:07.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think the Miss might face \Nadversity because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At any rate, I'll think of a \Nway to repay my debt quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, there's the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:20.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't yet know what the \Nmeaning of my life is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but right now, I just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone... who tries to make you cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that... be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Is this gonna become \Na battle anime startin' next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The boy shook free of uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:01.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and found meaning in his life, \Nprotecting his mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In which direction does butler \NHayate's tomorrow lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:08.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, he will be fighting \Nwith all kinds of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose that pendant, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria has gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this? You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't gotten my \Npocket change, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, how do you plan to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and the others are over there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all left me here all by my lonesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.18,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Wooooooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cold era this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:57.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:57.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:08.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:08.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:11.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:11.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:17.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:17.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:33.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:33.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:54.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:54.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:23:00.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:23:00.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:05.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:05.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:10.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:10.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:14.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:14.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:25.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:25.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:26.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:27.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.98,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,240)}Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:34.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, our week of being \Nreinforced by Maria ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It does?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:39.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next time, that hugely \Npopular character will be appearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:43.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that possibly be the #1 in \Npopularity polls? That Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:44.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:48.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, it will be Nagi's turn \Non duty starting next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, this is the end of my week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:52.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I being treated \Nawfully poorly for all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time with keen interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:56.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:59.25,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is that you, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:23:59.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Nishizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:19.27,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:00.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each other since Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world have you \Nbeen doing since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot of things happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:06.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working as a butler \Nat a certain mansion, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:11.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'm glad. I'm really \Nhappy that I got to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.95,0:24:13.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Long Ago, We Learned from a Space Sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.71,0:24:17.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"that Being Young is About Not Looking Back".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:19.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:21.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My... My feelings for you are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:22.27,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Long Ago, We Learned from a Space Sheriff \Nthat Being Young is About Not Looking Back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:23.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to see Newtypes in combat!
